OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,FThe heat-health alert for the South
OL,7,FWest has been escalated from yellow to
OL,8,Famber and extended until Thursday 28
OL,9,FMay.
OL,11,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,12,Fhas warned that high temperatures pose
OL,13,Fan increased risk to vulnerable people
OL,14,Fand has reminded health and social
OL,15,Fcare services to prepare as
OL,16,Ftemperatures continue to rise, peaking
OL,17,Fat 33 degrees in some parts of the
OL,18,Fregion.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
