CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779865531
OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,FWith the amber heat-health alert in
OL,7,Fplace until 5pm on Thursday, the UKHSA
OL,8,Fsays that the South West's coastline,
OL,9,Frivers and open water present
OL,10,Fadditional risks during hot weather.
OL,12,FPeople are advised to swim only at
OL,13,Fdesignated, supervised locations and
OL,14,Fto keep a close eye on children near
OL,15,Fany open water.
OL,17,FJacq Hardwick specialises in water
OL,18,Fsafety at Avon Fire and Rescue and is
OL,19,Fhosting activities in Weston-Super-
OL,20,FMare this week to share tips on
OL,21,Favoiding dangers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
