OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779865531
OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,FShe told ITV West Country: "There is
OL,7,Fsinking mud. Here at Weston, we have
OL,8,Fthe second-highest tidal range in the
OL,9,Fworld. The tide comes in really
OL,10,Fquickly and it can catch people
OL,11,Funaware."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779865531
OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,FShe explained: "There were about 40
OL,7,Frescues yesterday (Monday 25 May) and
OL,8,Fthat is just in one day alone. I know
OL,9,Fit was incredibly hot yesterday, but
OL,10,Fwe are set now for a really, really
OL,11,Fhot week. So we would urge people -
OL,12,Fplease keep yourselves safe on the
OL,13,Fbeach. Be aware that the mud is a
OL,14,Fdanger and don't go past those yellow
OL,15,Fwarning signs.
OL,17,F"Cold-water shock can affect even
OL,18,Fstrong swimmers when entering cold
OL,19,Fwater on a hot day, and water-related
OL,20,Fincidents typically increase during
OL,21,Fperiods of high temperature.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
