PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779865531
OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,FMeanwhile, James Berryman runs Penhale
OL,7,FCaravan and Camping Park in Fowey and
OL,8,Fsays that the heatwave has boosted
OL,9,Fbusiness over the last few days.
OL,11,FHe said: "Future bookings are looking
OL,12,Fdown this year, but we can just hope
OL,13,Ffor good weather.
OL,15,F"This has really helped this weekend -
OL,16,Fthe sun coming out. But we'll have to
OL,17,Fsee, because people are leaving it
OL,18,Fright until the last minute to make
OL,19,Fbookings."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779865531
OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,FHe added: "At the moment, people
OL,7,Fhaven't got any money to go camping."
OL,9,FJulie Frost came to the campsite from
OL,10,FStaffordshire and said visiting
OL,11,FCornwall to enjoy the sun is a
OL,12,F"special" part of her life.
OL,14,FShe told ITV West Country: "I
OL,15,Fabsolutely love the hot weather, I
OL,16,Fcan't get enough of it. I've been here
OL,17,Fjust over a week and I'm actually
OL,18,Fgoing to be leaving around seven so I
OL,19,Fcan make the most of the day. I won't
OL,20,Fget back home until about midnight but
OL,21,Fto me that's worth it."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779865531
OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,FMark Taylor from Manchester agreed,
OL,7,Fpraising the region's views, scenery,
OL,8,Fcountryside, people and food.
OL,10,FHe said: "It's just a slower pace of
OL,11,Flife than city centre Manchester."
OL,13,FWhile the heat is boosting tourism,
OL,14,Fvisitors and locals are being reminded
OL,15,Fto stay cautious.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
