OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779865531
OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,FDr Chaam Klinger, Consultant in Health
OL,7,FProtection at UKHSA South West, said:
OL,8,F"We want those living in and visiting
OL,9,Fthe South West, particularly for half
OL,10,Fterm to enjoy the good weather this
OL,11,Fweek. However, we know that even
OL,12,Fmoderate heat can lead to serious
OL,13,Fhealth problems, especially for older
OL,14,Fpeople and those with certain health
OL,15,Fconditions, so it's important that
OL,16,Feveryone takes simple precautions
OL,17,Fwhile enjoying the warm weather over
OL,18,Fthe coming days.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
