PN,43309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779865531
OL,3,CHeat health alert escalated to amber
OL,4,Cfor South West, extended until Thursday
OL,6,F"If you have friends, family or
OL,7,Fneighbours who are more vulnerable, it
OL,8,Fis important to check in on them and
OL,9,Fensure they are aware of the forecasts
OL,10,Fand are following the necessary
OL,11,Fadvice."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
